OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy with some
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain during the morning.
OL,7,FBecoming drier with variable amounts
OL,8,Fof cloud and bright or sunny spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping into the afternoon. Feeling
OL,10,Fwarm and muggy. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA fine end to the day, with
OL,13,Fbright or sunny spells. Staying dry
OL,14,Fwith variable amounts of cloud and
OL,15,Fclear spells overnight. A warm and
OL,16,Fmuggy night. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
