OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FEarly cloud will soon thin
OL,6,Fand break up to give a mostly fine day
OL,7,Fwith bright or sunny spells for many.
OL,8,FFeeling very warm and muggy. Light
OL,9,Fwinds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMostly
OL,12,Ffine with some sunshine. Turning very
OL,13,Fwarm and humid towards the weekend,
OL,14,Fstaying mainly dry, but with a small
OL,15,Fchance of some scattered showers on
OL,16,FSaturday.
